column16: Billy Butler singles on a ground ball to center fielder Michael Bourn.
Manny Machado grounds out, shortstop Asdrubal Cabrera to first baseman Nick Swisher.
Brian Roberts lines out to right fielder Drew Stubbs.
Alexi Casilla walks.   J.   Hardy to 2nd.
Nate McLouth flies out to left fielder Michael Brantley in foul territory.
